      "message": "Line 2119: The retry callback silently returns when retries are exhausted after a previous failure (`state.exhausted`). That hides repeated failures in the same registration cycle and makes diagnostics difficult. Log at least once when an exhausted callback is ignored, or cancel/unregister the callback after exhaustion so the silence is intentional.\n```suggestion\n                if (state.exhausted) {\n                    JAMI_DEBUG(\"[Account {}] Identity announcement retry already exhausted\", thisPtr-\u003egetAccountID());\n                    return;\n                }\n```",
